title: Who Killed the Radio Star?
description: In this Dateline classic, weekend boaters just off California’s fabled Catalina island discover a body floating in the water. The victim turns out to be a well-known radio personality. What happened to Steven B. Williams? Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on June 3, 2012.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
